data.description: Searching for a 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom Ranch nestled in the heart of Greer? This home has everything you need to move straight in and start making memories! When arrive at the property, you will notice the spacious a 0.44+/- acre lot and inviting front porch. As soon as you step inside, you will notice how spacious and bright everything feels. The Open Concept Living Area is accentuated by cathedral ceilings, a gas fireplace, and large windows with views of the back yard. The Kitchen boasts elegant black and white granite countertops and comes equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a smooth top range, dishwasher, and microwave. The Breakfast Room is conveniently tucked in between the Kitchen and Living Room, with plenty of space for your favorite table and chairs. Additional bar seating at the island provides even more room to gather. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or love to entertain, this kitchen is a true delight! The first two bedrooms are at the front of the home, as is the first bathroom and spacious Foyer. These bedrooms provide versatile spaces that can also be personalized to suit your needs and could easily be used as a home office, cozy guest room, gaming space, or a creative studio. The Master Suite is toward the rear of the home and is a serene escape with its own private en-suite bathroom which includes double sinks, inviting garden tub, separate shower, and a dreamy walk-in closet. The two-car garage offers ample storage space and protection for your vehicles, as well as secure access to your home in inclement weather. Your tour concludes as you explore the outdoor spaces. The beautiful backyard is the perfect backdrop for outdoor relaxation, gardening, and entertaining. It's easy to imagine yourself chatting with friends around the grill on cool evenings or soaking up the sun's warmth on quiet mornings. The convenient location of this home also means you can enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as nearby parks and recreation in Greer. Don't miss this rare opportunity to turn this charming property into your new abode. Schedule your showing today!
